<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Murrain" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Murrain,</orth> an infectious disease among cattle; used as a curse: <cit><quote>a m. on your monster,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.2.88" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 2, 88</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a red m. o' thy jade's tricks,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 2.1.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 1, 20</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a m. on't,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.5.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 5, 3</bibl></cit>. In <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids II, 1, 97</bibl> some M. Edd. <emph>m.,</emph> O. Edd. <emph>murrion.</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>